About
Stick War really stored a good shelf of memories in our
childhood. It was and is very pleasant to see that the game is
still on, especially with the newest series Stick War 3 game, It
is sadly also the last series of the stick war series. Lets record
our moments shall we? This channel is dedicated for Stick
war, Stick war 2, Stick war 3, Stick war legacy , Stick
empires. It is highly possible that we will change our
"playground", (target game) after a while to maybe other
Flash games and stick games. But we will stay on Stick war
series for a while. This channel is also dedicated to other
things that are going in the fandom (The stickdom? is a good
name?) for example mods, changes, effects. But also more
importantly we are focusing on to make our videos funny....
About the webpage:
Making this was not really that easy as just making a freaking
a YouTube channel, Please subscribe to the channel.
